<div id="contentBlock">

  <div id="contentBlockHeader">
    <%= image_tag("/images/me.png", :class => "avatar") %>
    <p>Hey everyone, thanks for dropping in and checking out my stuff. I'm mainly an AS3/Flash platform developer, but I also do quite a bit with Objective-C/iOS, Javascript, CSS, PHP, and Rails too. Below are a few samples of my work.</p>
  </div>
  
  <ul class="collapsedList"> 

    <% @items.each_with_index do |item, index| %>
        <li>
          <div class="contentItem">
            <%= image_tag(item.thumbnail_url) %>
            <div class="description" id="item-<%= index %>">
              <p class="invisible"><%= item.description %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
    <% end %>
    
  </ul>
  
  <script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function() {
      cldn.data(<%= @items_json.html_safe %>);
    });
  </script>

  <div class="clearList"/>
</div>


